name: Goodfood Market Corp. 5.75% convertible unsecured subordinated debentures
longDescription: Goodfood Market Corp. is a Canada-based online grocery company. The Company is focused on delivering fresh meal solutions, add-ons , and grocery items for members from across Canada. It provides its customers with access to fresh and delicious products, as well as pricing by its culinary team and direct-to-consumer infrastructure and technology. It connects its partner farms and suppliers to its customers kitchens directly. Its production facilities are located in the provinces of Quebec and Alberta.
